name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: My family and I wish all Arkansans a #MerryChristmas and #HappyHolidays!  https://t.co/3Y2ypGzOWs

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: My thoughts and prayers go out to the @BryantPolice officer shot in the line of duty and to their family during this difficult time. Our law enforcement officers risk their lives to keep our communities safe and I’m grateful for their service.  https://t.co/T5uBFgjwFL

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: I wish all Arkansans a #MerryChristmas & #HappyHolidays! Let’s remember our servicemembers & first responders who sacrifice so much for our safety & security. I pray the Lord blesses you & that you enjoy this time with friends & family. I look forward to serving you in 2020!  https://t.co/k2VGN6NEpA

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: #US & #Arkansas business, farmers, & workers need #USMCANow! Our federal delegation has led on this w/@POTUS @realDonaldTrump, but I urge #Congress to ratify this much needed agreement to increase fair trade & expand markets for #ArkAg & business. #arpx  https://t.co/JrNNACvp2P

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: Congrats to @SlimChickens on opening your 100th location today in W. Little Rock! Great home-grown AR company. I ordered my favorite: chicken sandwich dipped (special request...just ask) in inferno sauce & topped w/ more inferno, Cayenne ranch, & blue cheese sauces!  https://t.co/O1jk4gQqdp

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: Thank you @realdonaldtrump for @whitehouse Christmas Party hospitality. Look who I ran into!  Old ball coach @CoachLouHoltz88!  We had good talk about Holtz and the Hogs! #WPS  https://t.co/VfTtfR05lV

tweet: Fun facts about @UFC fighter @ThugnastyMMA Bryce Mitchell: he’s majoring in economics at @HardingU & studying Adam Smith’s Wealth of Nations. He trains at @westsidemma right here in central AR, and he’s a big fan of President @realDonaldTrump!  https://t.co/UkaE6m5oMU

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: Today we celebrated the life of Officer Stephen Carr of the @FYVpolice Dept. The tremendous outpouring of support shows that Officer Carr’s legacy of service & sacrifice will not be forgotten. Please continue to pray for his family & friends.  https://t.co/goMy9HrIN0

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: Great to see Arkansas’s own @ThugnastyMMA Bryce Mitchell fresh off his big @UFC win. In case you missed his post-fight interview, he’s a big fan of President @realDonaldTrump!  https://t.co/gkGTEBs9Hc

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: It was a pleasure to preside over the @ARStateChamber’s @LeadershipAR mock legislative session & speak to participants about how to have a positive impact on the political process. This is a great program that attracts some of AR’s most talented young leaders.  https://t.co/yfhQmg6Bam

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: The announcement to move forward on #USMCA is exciting news for #AR businesses & #ArkAg products. I applaud the work of our federal delegation & @realDonaldTrump. This was one of @POTUS’ top priorities & it means free & fair trade & expanded markets for our businesses. #arpx  https://t.co/wp60AX2C1R

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: Had a fun weekend attending @ArkansasGuard Christmas lunch at Camp Robinson, 35th annual @ToysForTotsUSA run, & visiting w/ local chapter of @DFCSociety. Busy weekend!  https://t.co/Tu8pbHfw30

name: Lt. Gov. Tim Griffin
tweet: #ShopSmall/#Shoplocal for #SmallBusinessSaturday! Small businesses are the backbone of the economy & they invest & grow jobs in #Arkansas. I am thankful for hard work & dedication of #Smallbiz owners & entrepreneurs in #AR. Thanks @NFIB/@nfib_ar for being the voice of #smallbiz.
